%p Voice Republic's payment concept is as simple as it gets:

%ul
  %li No subscription fees, no recurring costs.

  %li
    No distinction between stream, upload or archiving costs - the
    purchase of a credit includes all features: live streaming or
    uploading to the archive as well as various share options: podcast
    download, embedded player, digital flyer for Twitter, Facebook and
    mail share etc.

%p Credits do not expire!
